#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"We offer a 30-day return policy for\n"
"                                                                all "
"furniture items. Products must\n"
"                                                                be in their "
"original condition,\n"
"                                                                unused, and "
"include the receipt or\n"
"                                                                proof of "
"purchase. Refunds are\n"
"                                                                processed "
"within 5-7 business days\n"
"                                                                after we "
"receive the returned item."
msgstr ""
"我们为所有家具产品提供30天退货政策\n"
"                                                                。产品\n"
"                                                                必须保持未使"
"用过的原始状态\n"
"                                                                ，并附上收据"
"或购买凭证。\n"
"                                                                我们将在\n"
"                                                                收到退回商品"
"后的5-7个工作日\n"
"                                                                内处理退款。"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_3972
