"We'd love to hear from you! If you have any\n"
"                                            questions, feedback, or need "
"assistance, please feel\n"
"                                            free to reach out to us using "
"the contact details\n"
"                                            provided. Our team is here to "
"help and will respond as\n"
"                                            soon as possible. Thank you for "
"getting in touch!"
msgstr ""
"我们期待您的来信！\n"
"                                            如果您有任何问题、反馈或需要帮"
"助，请随时\n"
"                                            通过所提供的联系方式与我们联"
"系。\n"
"                                            我们的团队随时准备为您提供帮"
"助，\n"
"                                            并将尽快回复。感谢您的联系！"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"We're here to assist you,\n"
"                                                day and night."
msgstr ""
"无论白天黑夜，\n"
"                                                我们随时为您提供协助。"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
