"                                                                解决方案，以"
"确保\n"
"                                                                您的满意。"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When a customer fills out your contact form, Odoo automatically creates an "
"<b>opportunity</b> in the <b>CRM App</b>. This makes it simple to "
"communicate with the client, address their specific needs, and even "
"<b>create a tailored quotation</b> directly from the CRM."
msgstr ""
"当客户填写您的联系表格时，Odoo会在<b> CRM应用程序</b>中自动创建<b>商机</b>。"
"这使与客户交流，满足他们的特定需求变得简单，甚至直接从CRM<b>创建量身定制的报"
"价</b>。"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
